Class patient

java.lang.Object
patient
public class patient extends Object
Alaa Khan CEN 3024C - 13950 - Software Development 1 November 12, 2025 patient.java This is a constructor class. It creates a default constructor, so it does not take in any parameters. This is so that the patient object can be created, but its fields will be populated later based on the user's input.
